What is a Todo list?
-> A Todo list is a list of todos 
------
What can be done with a todo list?
-> Add item to the list
-> Show current todos in the list
-> Check any todo 
-> Remove any todo from the list
-> Update the todo list

Where to store the todos?
-> Todos will be stored inside a file in a specific format
{
  todos: [
    { 
      name: "I have to do it by tommorow",
      priority: "H",
      Date: 20/5/2023
    }
  ]
}

What is a todo?
{
  name: "Do this",
  priority: "H/L/M",
  Date: dd/mm/yyyy
}

Change todo name
Change the date of the todo 
change priority

How the user will interact with the system?
  node main.js todos
  node main.js add "I have to do this" "H" "Date"
  node main.js mark <number>
  node main.js unmark <number>
  ndoe main.js delete <number>
